SQL_STMT_U.val: select z.BE_ID BE_ID, SUM(z.AANTAL) AANTAL from (select b.be_volgnummer BE_ID, case when c.ts_koop_verkoop_ind = 1 and tr.trai_tr_account_code = 1 or c.ts_koop_verkoop_ind = 2 and tr.trai_tr_account_code = 3 then 1 else -1 end * case when b.be_aantal_cijfers_display <> 0 then b.be_prijs_factor else 1 end * a.tr_aantal AANTAL from TV_TRANSACTIONS_IN_PROGRESS tv inner join TV_TRIP_REL_ACCOUNT_INFO tr on tr.trai_tr_volgnummer = tv.trip_tr_volgnummer inner join TRANSAKTIES a on a.tr_volgnummer = tv.trip_tr_volgnummer inner join BELEGGINGSINSTRUMENT b on b.be_volgnummer = tv.trip_tr_be_volgnummer inner join TRANSACTIESOORTEN c on c.ts_symbool = a.tr_indicatie where (tr.TRAI_TRIP_TR_STATUS_BIT = 1 OR a.tr_transnummer = 0) and tr.trai_tr_re_id = ~1 and tr.trai_tr_account_code in (1, 3) and b.be_bi_nummer between 100 and 299 UNION ALL select b.be_volgnummer BE_ID, case when b.be_aantal_cijfers_display <> 0 then b.be_prijs_factor else 1 end * p.ap_saldo_positie AANTAL from aktuele_posities p inner join BELEGGINGSINSTRUMENT b on b.be_volgnummer = p.ap_be_volgnummer where p.ap_re_id = ~1 and p.ap_saldo_positie <> 0 and b.be_bi_nummer between 100 and 299) z group by z.BE_ID order by z.BE_ID
